webpackJsonp([84440872678790],{8321:function(e,a){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"New Year",date:"01 Jan 2006",slug:"/2006-01-01-new-year/",tags:"Y2006"},html:'<p>We\'ve been busy this week, with Christmas, Christopher\'s birthday, and his Grandmother visiting for 2 weeks. We spent New Years Eve at home and managed to hit a number of <a href="http://german.about.com/library/blsilvester.htm">German New Year\'s Customs</a>, eating raclette (with enough leftovers for a repeat performance tonight), drinking <em>Feuerzangenbowle</em>, and watching <a href="http://www.slate.com/id/2133551">"Dinner For One"</a> (twice). We skipped the <em>Bleigiessen</em> and the jelly doughnuts. Christopher and I instead napped for a bit before midnight to rest up for the fireworks. Sounds like our evening was pretty much like at <a href="http://justcallmemausi.blogspot.com/2005/12/einen-guten-rutsch-in-das-neue-jahr.html">Christina\'s</a>, where you can read what the New Year\'s greeting "Guten Rutsch" really means.</p>\n<p>Alas, tomorrow is the start of a normal work and kindergarten week. Mama even gets to fly to Munich overnight to start the year. Grandma will be here all week, though.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Equality of the Sexes",date:"01 Jan 2006",slug:"/2006-01-01-equality-of-the-sexes/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Snow Angel",date:"01 Jan 2006",slug:"/2006-01-01-snow-angel/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Equality of the Sexes",date:"01 Jan 2006",slug:"/2006-01-01-equality-of-the-sexes/",tags:"Y2006"},html:'<blockquote>The German women\'s team has already won the World Cup, and I don\'t see any reason why men cannot achieve the same as women.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Chancellor Merkel on the 2006 World Cup in her <a href="http://www.bundesregierung.de/-,413.940270/pressemitteilung/Neujahrsansprache-von-Bundeska.htm" title="REGIERUNGonline - Neujahrsansprache von Bundeskanzlerin Angela Merkel">New Year\'s Address</a>. By the way, her daily calendar is available as an <a href="http://bundeskanzlerin.de/bk/Navigation/Service/rss.html">RSS feed</a>.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Happy Landings!",date:"31 Dec 2005",slug:"/2005-12-31-happy-landings/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"New Year",date:"01 Jan 2006",slug:"/2006-01-01-new-year/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Happy Landings!",date:"31 Dec 2005",slug:"/2005-12-31-happy-landings/",tags:"Y2005"},html:'<p><a href="http://www.hawkin.com/rkMain.asp?PAGEID=20670&STK_PROD_CODE=08720" title="Hawkin\'s Bazaar Product Detail- 08720: Champichute"><img src="http://www.papascott.de/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2005/12/champichute.gif" border="0" height="145" width="145" alt="champichute.gif" align="right" /></a> Here\'s wishing everyone a happy and soft landing in 2006! (The <a href="http://www.hawkin.com/rkMain.asp?PAGEID=20670&STK_PROD_CODE=08720" title="Hawkin\'s Bazaar Product Detail- 08720: Champichute">Champichute</a> is <a href="http://java.blogg.de/eintrag.php?id=226" title="I wish you all a Successful and Happy New Year! [the egoist]">via Cem</a>.)</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Never Ending Holidays",date:"26 Dec 2005",slug:"/2005-12-26-never-ending-holidays/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Equality of the Sexes",date:"01 Jan 2006",slug:"/2006-01-01-equality-of-the-sexes/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:253,pageCount:1101}}}});
